#
# Both agents own everything. An author cannot approve their own PR, so each
# agent's PR requires the OTHER agent's approval → mutual review, no deadlock:
#   - Claude PRs (author @hallovorld)      need @haorensjtu-dev (Codex) approval
#   - Codex  PRs (author @haorensjtu-dev)  need @hallovorld approval
#
# Pairs with branch-protection require_code_owner_reviews=true, which is enabled
# AFTER this file lands on main (see doc/progress/2026-06-19-codeowners-review-gate.md).
# Enabling the setting before this is on main would lock ALL merges.
